5月30日18時，經青海省民政廳、公安廳和玉樹州政府按相關程序規定核准，玉樹地震已造成2698人遇難，其中已確認身份2687人，無名屍體11具，失蹤270人。已確認身份的遇難人員：男性1290人，女性1397人；青海玉樹籍2537人，省內非玉樹籍54人，外省籍96人；遇難學生199人<ref name="diednumber" />。其中，殉難者中包括[[香港|香港]][[義工|義工]][[黃福榮|黃福榮]]，成功救出了三名学生和一名老师。当他尝试救出另外两名老师时，却遇上余震，最终不幸死亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/disaster/20100416-Hong-Kong-91019969.html|title=港人青海遇难引发反思中国扶贫运动|work=美国之音|date=2010-04-16|accessdate=2010-04-20}}{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。由于遇难者太多已经无法进行藏人传统的天葬，4月17日开始火化上千具遇难者的遗体。火葬仪式在[[结古寺|结古寺]]附近的天葬台进行。地震发生几天来，喇嘛们做了字幅、面条麻花和糌粑为死者诵经超度。

当地土木结构的房屋倒塌严重，70%学校房屋垮塌<ref>{{cite web | language = Zh-Hans | publisher = 中国广播网 | title = 玉树州红十字会称玉树70%学校房屋垮塌 | url = http://news.163.com/10/0414/22/6491G37K0001124J.html | author =  | date = 2010-04-14 | accessdate = 2010-04-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100418070802/http://news.163.com/10/0414/22/6491G37K0001124J.html | archivedate = 2010-04-18 }}</ref>。很多人被埋在瓦砾之下，包括不少学生<ref name="voa">{{cite web|url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/CHINA-EARTHQUAKE-20100414-90817169.html|title=青海玉树县强震 四百多人死上万人伤|work=美国之音|date=2010-04-14|accessdate=2010-04-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100416142728/http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/CHINA-EARTHQUAKE-20100414-90817169.html|archivedate=2010-04-16}}</ref>。15000户民房倒塌，10万灾民需要转移安置<ref name="voa0415">{{cite web|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/article-20100415-death-rises--qinghai-quake-90933119/466084.html|title=中国地震617人遇难 总理抵灾区|work=美国之音|date=2010-04-15|accessdate=2010-04-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118012223/https://www.voachinese.com/a/article-20100415-death-rises--qinghai-quake-90933119/466084.html|archivedate=2018-01-18}}</ref> 15日 16 时，统计地震造成760人遇难，243人失踪，11477人受伤<ref>{{cite web | language = zh | publisher = 网易（转自青海新闻网） | title = 青海玉树地震已造成760人死亡243人失踪 | url = http://news.163.com/10/0416/00/64BO0QVP0001124J.html | author =  | date = 2010-04-16 | accessdate = 2010-04-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100419071157/http://news.163.com/10/0416/00/64BO0QVP0001124J.html | archivedate = 2010-04-19 }}</ref>。此外，强震令一个公园中的佛塔塔顶整个倒下<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.163.com/10/0414/11/647QG4RU00014AEE.html|title=玉树一公园佛塔塔顶整个倒下|work=台海网|publisher=网易|date=2010-04-14|accessdate=2010-04-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419002503/http://news.163.com/10/0414/11/647QG4RU00014AEE.html|archivedate=2010-04-19}}</ref>。一座水库出现裂缝，当地民众只能采取放水等措施<ref name="voa" />。电信方面，玉树县固定电话中断<ref name="voa" />，供电、通信一度中断。[[国家电网|国家电网]]青海分公司目前派出四批次抢修人员480多人，进行震区的电网抢修工作<ref>{{cite web | language = Zh-Hans | publisher = 网易探索 | title = 连线国家电网:今晚将定出玉树电网抢修最佳方案 | url = http://discover.news.163.com/10/0415/19/64B7QD4K000125LI.html | author =  | date = 2010-04-15 | accessdate = 2010-04-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160927073822/http://discover.news.163.com/10/0415/19/64B7QD4K000125LI.html | archivedate = 2016-09-27 }}</ref>。此外，当地的水受到污染，导致灾民急需饮水和食品<ref name="bbc0415">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/04/100415_quake_rescue.shtml|title=卫生部通知救援谨防灾区瘟疫爆发|work=BBC|date=2010-04-15|accessdate=2010-04-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100422115837/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/04/100415_quake_rescue.shtml|archivedate=2010-04-22}}</ref>。

== 响应与救援 ==
=== 救援行动 ===
震后，灾区群众展开自救行动。拥有3000余名学生的玉树县第三完全小学80%房屋倒塌，数十名教师徒手挖掘废墟展开救援。61名儿童被从废墟中挖出，其中34人死亡<ref>{{cite web | language = Zh-Hans | publisher = 人民网 | title = 震区老师徒手挖出61名学生 34名已死亡 | url = http://news.163.com/10/0415/08/64A2DNHN000146BC.html | author =  | date = 2010-04-15 | accessdate = 2010-04-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100418071050/http://news.163.com/10/0415/08/64A2DNHN000146BC.html | archivedate = 2010-04-18 }}</ref>。此外，结古镇地处[[藏传佛教|藏传佛教]]范围，大量青海、甘肃、四川僧侣也参与到救援中。当地[[结古寺|结古寺]]僧侣下山配合部队展开救援，一百公里的四川[[甘孜州|甘孜州]][[色须寺|色须寺]]也派出五百名僧侣参与救援，并在废墟中挖出60名幸存者<ref>{{cite web | language = zh | publisher = 新京报 | title = 500僧侣挖出60名幸存者 | url = http://news.163.com/10/0417/02/64EGUP9500014AED.html | author =  | date = 2010-04-17 | accessdate = 2010-04-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100421221857/http://news.163.com/10/0417/02/64EGUP9500014AED.html | archivedate = 2010-04-21 }}</ref>。玉树附近[[囊谦县|囊谦县]]和[[甘孜州|甘孜州]][[白玉寺|白玉寺]]等寺庙的上千名僧侣立即赶赴灾区协助进行救灾。附近几百公里打工的建筑工人，也携带自己工具和车辆也展开救援<ref>{{cite web | language = Zh-Hans | publisher = 中国广播网 | title = 震区直击:当地僧侣下山帮助挖掘尸体 | url = http://news.163.com/10/0415/07/649V9FEG000146BC.html | author =  | date = 2010-04-15 | accessdate = 2010-04-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100418071014/http://news.163.com/10/0415/07/649V9FEG000146BC.html | archivedate = 2010-04-18 }}</ref>。美国之音报道称，从甘孜赶来救援、20辆面包车载满的僧尼是最重要的救援力量。

2010年4月14日，[[中共中央总书记|中共中央总书记]][[胡锦涛|胡锦涛]]，[[国务院总理|国务院总理]][[温家宝|温家宝]]要求全力救援灾民并委托[[中华人民共和国国务院副总理|副总理]][[回良玉|回良玉]]前往灾区慰问与指挥救援行动<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2010-04/14/c_1233351.htm|title=胡锦涛温家宝对青海玉树抗震救灾工作作出重要指示|work=新华网|date=2010-04-14|accessdate=2010-04-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100417090725/http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2010-04/14/c_1233351.htm|archivedate=2010-04-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2010-04/15/c_1233892.htm|title=回良玉深入青海玉树地震重灾区组织指挥抗震救灾工作|work=新华网|date=2010-04-14|accessdate=2010-04-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100417132226/http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2010-04/15/c_1233892.htm|archivedate=2010-04-17}}</ref>。温家宝推迟原定于4月22日至25日对[[文莱|文莱]]、[[印尼|印尼]]和[[缅甸|缅甸]]的正式访问<ref>{{cite web | language = Zh-Hans | publisher = 网易（转自中国新闻网） | title = 胡锦涛将提前结束外访回国 温家宝推迟出访 | url = http://news.163.com/10/0415/20/64BB7TKP000146BD.html | author = 张朔 | date = 2010-04-15 | accessdate = 2010-04-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100419004231/http://news.163.com/10/0415/20/64BB7TKP000146BD.html | archivedate = 2010-04-19 }}</ref>，并于4月15日晚，乘专机抵达青海玉树地震灾区指挥救援<ref>{{cite web | language = Zh-Hans | publisher = 网易（转自中国广播网） | title = 温家宝抵达青海玉树地震灾区 | url = http://news.163.com/10/0415/18/64B4G372000146BC.html | author =  | date = 2010-04-15 | accessdate = 2010-04-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100418021317/http://news.163.com/10/0415/18/64B4G372000146BC.html | archivedate = 2010-04-18 }}</ref>。

